title: #92Noon at Windsong! Zucker/Rosenfels/Rudolph/Greenway/Russo
description: #92Noon is LIVE at from 10th Annual Champions for Children event, benefiting the University of Minnesota Health Masonic Children's Hospital! Michael Russo calls in to talk about the latest NHL news, Jason Zucker is in attendance and discusses the latest on his contract negotiations, Sage Rosenfels hangs out for a while and gives insight on his final year as a Viking and plenty more!
